channel.title: Why does my items is clue scroll?
channel.description: I've downloaded a source and check the item.cfg and saw bandos godsword when i put like ::pickup the id for bandos and the amount it came out as a clue scroll -.- :|

item.title: Why does my items is clue scroll?
item.dc:creator: @jc22493 Jc22493
item.description:
@jc22493 wrote:

Maybe your pickup doesn’t go up to the ID number that the bandos godsword was. Most old servers only go up to 10000, nothing over 4 digits.
